<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-01-26T13:35:00-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-01-26T13:35:00-05:00</published><updated> 2024-01-26T13:35:00-05:00</updated><title>这是每个开发者都会讨厌的新苹果税</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;浅绿色和深绿色背景上的 Apple 徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3nKbjbIHtQYfWANGCgxO1CQV4ek=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73087669/STK071_apple_K_Radtke_03.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;4dVRyx&quot;>;Apple 终于向欧盟的第三方应用商店开放 iPhone，开启了一个充满活力、笨重且不拘一格的市场其应用程序生态系统的新时代。至少，这可能会发生，具体取决于开发者如何应对一个既微小又巨大的障碍：0.50 欧元的费用。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;BmE2zR&quot;>;Apple 正在为那些想要在这些第三方商店上运营。从表面上看，这看起来很棒：如果应用程序通过第三方商店分发，则无需向苹果支付销售分成。如果开发者仍然希望通过 Apple 的 App Store 进行分发，则费用将从传统的 30% 降至 17%。对于符合条件的“小型企业”应用程序，费用甚至更低，从原来的 15% 下调...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/26 /24051823/apple-third-party-app-stores-50-cent-fee&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/26/24051823/apple-third-party-app-stores-50-cent-fee" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/26/24051823/apple-third-party-app-stores-50-cent-fee</id><author><name>雅各布·卡斯特雷纳克斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-01-26T13:07:14-05:00</published><updated> 2024-01-26T13:07:14-05:00</updated><title> 《猴人》的新预告片感觉就像是向约翰·威克发出的警告枪</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/WPv6DlLAJouRkQUnRvh97IVyn8c=/547x0:2332x1190/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73087559 /Screen_Shot_2024_01_26_at_12.04.38_PM.0.png&quot; />; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;3VrnDr&quot;>;在过去的几年里，狮门影业一直主导着时尚、精心设计、充满弹孔的动作惊悚片类型， &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23739025/john-wick-5-lionsgate-early-development&quot;>;源源不断&lt;/a>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/23641526/john-wick-chapter-4-review-keanu-reeves&quot;>;&lt;em>;疾速追杀&lt;/em>;电影&lt;/a>;以及&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2023/9/20/23879184/the-Continental-john-wick-peacock-review&quot;>;衍生系列&lt;/a>;。但导演戴夫·帕特尔 (Dev Patel) 为环球影业和布鲁姆豪斯 (Blumhouse) 制作的&lt;em>;猴人&lt;/em>;的第一部预告片让观众们明白，这类电影可以有多么宏大、狂野和更具视觉灵感，这似乎是一个光荣的挑战。&lt; /p>; &lt;p id=&quot;7t6ZOV&quot;>;以现代孟买的街道为背景，&lt;em>;猴人&lt;/em>;讲述了一个名叫基德（帕特尔饰）的男人的故事，他是一名有前科的人，后来重返社会残酷地提醒人们，印度的种姓制度如何让贫穷、脆弱的人们陷入暴力和系统性贫困的循环之中。孩子对田园诗般的童年有着美好的回忆...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24051748/monkey-man-trailer-universal-blumhouse-dev-patel -jordan-peele&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24051748/monkey-man-trailer-universal-blumhouse-dev-patel-jordan-peele" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24051748/monkey-man-trailer-universal-blumhouse-dev-patel-jordan-peele</id><author><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-01-26T12:41:50-05:00</published><updated> 2024-01-26T12:41:50-05:00</updated><title>微软解释俄罗斯黑客如何监视其高管</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;微软徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/rePcBJk_QRgZjGDX3j2oNGSwvS4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73087467/STK095_Microsoft_04.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ttXXlq&quot;>;Microsoft &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2024/1/19/24044561/microsoft-senior-leadership-emails-hack- Russian-security-attack&quot;>;上周透露&lt;/a>;发现俄罗斯国家对其企业系统发起民族国家攻击- &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2020/12/13/22173035/hackers-Russia-breached-us-government-agcies-email-cozy-bear&quot;>;SolarWinds 攻击背后的赞助黑客&lt;/a>;。黑客能够访问微软高级领导团队的一些成员的电子邮件帐户 - 可能会监视他们数周或数月。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;XTIIjt&quot;>;虽然微软在周五晚些时候首次向 SEC 披露的信息中没有提供有关攻击者如何获得访问权限的详细信息，但该软件制造商现在已经&lt;a href=&quot;https://click .linksynergy.com/deeplink?id=nOD%2FrLJHOac&amp;amp;mid=24542&amp;amp;u1=verge&amp;amp;murl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fsecurity%2Fblog%2F2024%2F01%2F25%2Fmidnight -blizzard-guidance-for-responders-on-nation-state-attack%2F&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;发布了关于黑客如何突破其安全性的初步分析&lt;/a>;。它还警告同一个黑客组织，称为 Nobelium 或“午夜暴雪”&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/4/19/23689456/microsoft-weather-cybersecurity-threat- actor-naming&quot;>;以天气为主题的&lt;/a>;绰号微软指的是他们，一直针对其他组织。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;NO8BWt&quot;>;N...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/26/24051708/microsoft-hack- Russian-security-attack-senior-leadership-emails&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/26/24051708/microsoft-hack-russian-security-attack-senior-leadership-emails" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/26/24051708/microsoft-hack- Russian-security-attack-senior-leadership-emails</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-01-26T12:12:30-05:00</published><updated> 2024-01-26T12:12:30-05:00</updated><title> Pixel 8 Pro 是一种愚蠢的测量体温的方法</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google Pixel 8 Pro，海湾蓝色，浅粉色背景，周围环绕着蓝色塑料方块&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/rmtFhgtoZMPXu73YU1sBzuP-E0o=/21x0: 1980x1306/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73087384/DSC05741.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;将温度传感器放在后面......当然是机身的选择温度扫描。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Allison Johnson / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;tAxDFI&quot;>;本周早些时候，Google &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/24/24049669 /google-pixel-8-pro-feature-drop-circle-to-search-update&quot;>;更新了 Pixel 8 Pro&lt;/a>;，让它奇怪的新型温度传感器终于可以读取人体读数了。&lt;strong>;&lt;/ strong>;我很遗憾地通知您，使用后，它并没有实现此功能&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23903842/pixel-8-pro-Temperature-sensor-fda-feature &quot;>;不再那么令人困惑&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;SNzZiO&quot;>;要测量体温，您必须将手机的红外温度传感器扫过前额侧面，即颞动脉上方。到目前为止，这里没有什么特别奇怪的。就在这个月，我查看了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/7/24022955/withings-beamo-multiscope-telehealth-ces-2024&quot;>;Withings BeamO&lt;/ a>;，一款 4 合 1 多功能示波器，您还可以在同一条动脉上扫描同一种传感器来测量体温。不同之处在于 BeamO 非常容易使用，而 Pixel 8 Pro 则极其挑剔。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot; >; &lt;cite>;屏幕截图：Richard Lawler / The Verge&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;你...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/24051531/pixel-8-pro-body-Temperature-thermometer-app”>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24051531/pixel-8-pro-body-temperature-thermometer-app" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24051531/pixel-8-pro-body-Temperature-thermometer-app</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-01-26T12:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2024-01-26T12:00:00-05:00</updated><title> Switch 2：有关任天堂下一代游戏机的所有新闻和谣言</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一双手拿着带有霓虹红和蓝色 Joy-Con 控制器的 Nintendo Switch 游戏机，在手持模式下玩《超级马里奥：奥德赛》。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lRXJa7d43pu9PKtNjoP8R4pBNok=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73087301/akrales_171025_2091_0010.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;无论它叫什么，听起来它很快就会推出。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/24051677/nintendo-switch-2-pro-rumors-news&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24051677/nintendo-switch-2-pro-rumors-news" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24051677/nintendo-switch-2-pro-rumors-news</id><author><name>乔恩·波特</name><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name><name>汤姆·沃伦</name><name>阿什·帕里什</name><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name><name>理查德·劳勒</name><name>杰·彼得斯</name><name>萨姆·拜福德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-01-26T11:29:58-05:00</published><updated> 2024-01-26T11:29:58-05:00</updated><title> 50 美元以下的最佳科技礼物</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Twinkly Candies 挂在电视后面，散发着彩色灯光&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8ar84NW_-lhcgMC9B32mijpuwLk=/0x209:1318x1088/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/71987547/twinkycandies.15.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Twinkly 的智能灯串可以让任何房间看起来梦幻般，花费不到 50 美元。&lt;/em>; |图片：Twinkly&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ev25qd&quot;>;如果“预算友好”和“高品质”对您来说听起来很矛盾，那么您将会大吃一惊。事实证明，您可以购买许多很棒的礼物，而无需完全耗尽您的储蓄帐户，这使得您可以轻松地为您的周年纪念日、生日聚会或众多其他礼物挑选一份礼物 -全年都有各种活动。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;UhsGAe&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem -component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;25 美元以下的最佳科技礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23156368/best-cheap-tech- gadgets-under-25&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;便宜又不烂的东西&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23837448/cheap-gadgets-tools-tech-accessories-可穿戴设备&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;UgPPeK&quot;>;不过，即使有大量价格低于 50 美元的廉价商品，找到合适的礼物仍然很困难从中选择。这就是为什么我们整理了一系列高科技礼物创意，范围从 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo .com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1626075-REG%2Fkodak_da00239_m35_35mm_camera_with.html&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F23161828%2Fbest-cheap-tech-gadgets-under-50&quot; rel =&quot;赞助的 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;一次性相机&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Skullcandy-True-Wireless-Ear-Earbuds/dp/B09VM2TBZF?tag= theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned